ermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-greets-eu-council-president-ahead-ev-tariffs-taking-effect-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统下令缓和南海局势，军事参谋长表示</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-orders-de-escalation-south-china-sea-military-chief-says-2024-07-04/</link><description>马尼拉军事参谋长周四表示，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯已指示武装部队缓和南海紧张局势，这与中国和菲律宾官员最近举行的磋商一致。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:17:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-orders-de-escalation-south-china-sea-military-chief-says-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在泰国开设电动汽车工厂，这是东南亚首家电动汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-opens-ev-factory-thailand-first-southeast-asia-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国比亚迪周四在泰国开设了一家电动汽车工厂，这是该汽车制造商在东南亚的第一家工厂，东南亚是一个快速增长的区域电动汽车市场，比亚迪已成为该市场的主导者。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-opens-ev-factory-thailand-first-southeast-asia-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>随着气候变化加剧，中国警告将出现更热、更长时间的热浪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-weather-authority-warns-high-summer-temperatures-2024-07-04/</link><description>气象局周四警告称，由于气候变化，中国正面临更炎热、持续时间更长的热浪，以及更频繁和不可预测的暴雨，世界第二大经济体正准备迎接另一个炎热的夏季。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-weather-authority-warns-high-summer-temperatures-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰提议对南极洲进行较小规模的基地重建</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/antarctica-new-zealand-proposes-smaller-redevelopment-base-2024-07-04/</link><description>政府机构周四表示，新西兰已经提出了一项新的、规模较小的重建该国南极洲基地的提案，此前一项计划因预算超支而暂停。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:45:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/antarctica-new-zealand-proposes-smaller-redevelopment-base-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国扣押拖网渔船可能是心理战行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizure-trawler-may-be-act-psychological-warfare-2024-07-04/</link><description>台湾一名高级安全官员周四表示，中国扣押一艘在中国海岸附近进行非法捕鱼的台湾拖网渔船可能是北京的心理战行为，旨在进一步向台北施压。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:27:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizure-trawler-may-be-act-psychological-warfare-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市触及27个月新高，美元因降息押注而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-04/</link><description>亚洲股市周四触及 27 个月高点，因美国数据疲软缩小了 9 月份降息的可能性，提振债券和大宗商品，同时拖累美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 01:44:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：市场情绪明朗，流动性清淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯、辛纳在温网晋级，但路德却被淘汰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-medvedev-battle-wimbledon-ruud-shown-door-2024-07-03/</link><description>卫冕冠军卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯和头号种子扬尼克·辛纳在温布尔登第三轮比赛中采取了截然不同的路线，但八号种子卡斯帕·路德却无法找到出路，并在阴云密布的周三感到阴郁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-medvedev-battle-wimbledon-ruud-shown-door-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔军政府同意通过谈判修复与贝宁的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/niger-junta-agrees-talks-repair-ties-with-benin-2024-07-03/</link><description>尼日尔军政府已同意与贝宁两位前总统领导的贝宁政府进行谈判，以帮助恢复尼日尔去年政变导致边境关闭和中国支持的石油管道关闭后的关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/niger-junta-agrees-talks-repair-ties-with-benin-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商回应欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-03/</link><description>随着欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税预计将于周四生效，一些汽车制造商已决定采取反制措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>德国停止向中国出售大众燃气轮机业务的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-stops-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-2024-07-03/</link><description>德国内阁周三以安全理由为由，阻止了将大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司的燃气轮机业务出售给一家中国公司的计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-stops-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-2024-07-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>